  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Both voices on VA saw with 4x unison each. HAMMER at +0.95 — near-maximum LOVE merges the two unison stacks into a massive 8-oscillator supersaw wall. Filters linked, cutoff at 4200 Hz for warmth without darkness. Slow attack (0.6s) and golden ratio release (1.618s). Breathing LFO at 0.01 Hz (100-second cycle) with depth 0.3 creates glacial filter movement. CURRENT at 0.6 for wide stereo. The sound of a cathedral where every stone is singing.",
